{"tid":2365763,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中美創新科技模式顛倒？美媒：Facebook 正抄襲中國","createTime":"2021-01-14T04:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T05:31:56.000Z","uid":156254,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8d725546424efc02b6081ac27affe73fa112574e","tid":2365763,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:27:33.000Z","msg":"中美創新科技模式顛倒？美媒：Facebook 正抄襲中國<br />\n | 梁綺文, 梁綺文 | 13-01-2021 13:15 |   | <br />\n<br />\n中美科技戰持續，過往美國多次指控中國「竊取」美國科技、程式概念等，但有美國媒體認為此情況正在顛倒。以 Facebook 為例，旗下 Instagram 近年就推出了新功能 Reels，與 TikTok 幾乎一樣。<br />\n<br />\n過往美國多次指控中國「竊取」美國科技、程式概念等，有美媒卻指出此情況正在顛倒<br />\nInstagram 近年推出了新功能 Reels，與 TikTok 幾乎一樣<br />\n美國新書作者兼記者 Chris Stokel-Walker 指，Facebook 抄襲的同時渲染中國網絡威脅，做法虛偽<br />\n【相關報導】特朗普簽署行政命令 禁美國人與支付寶等 8 個中國手機 Apps 交易【下一頁】<br />\n<br />\n美國即將出版新書《TikTok Boom: China, the US and the Superpower Race for Social Media》（TikTok 的興起：中國，美國與超級大國社交媒體競賽）的作者 Chris Stokel-Walker 日前撰文，指矽谷近年抄襲中國同行。他直言 Facebook 抄襲的同時渲染中國網絡威脅，做法虛偽。<br />\n<br />\nWalker 指出，TikTok 出現之前互聯網上的主要企業幾乎都是美國企業。因此 Facebook CEO 朱克伯格採取「不能收購就抄襲」的模式，近年極力渲染中國網絡威脅，更遊說美國政客對 TikTok 出手。但另一方面，他又讓 Instagram 推出抄襲 TikTok 的功能。<br />\n<br />\nWalker 最後補充，說中國產業的典型化特徵，如山寨、抄襲等已在西方出現。因為朱克伯格，西方現在已出現了會審查和監管的中式互聯網。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2851414/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E9%A1%9B%E5%80%92%EF%BC%9F%E7%BE%8E%E5%AA%92%EF%BC%9AFacebook%20%E6%AD%A3%E6%8A%84%E8%A5%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2851414%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%25E9%25A1%259B%25E5%2580%2592%25EF%25BC%259F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25AA%2592%25EF%25BC%259AFacebook%2520%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%258A%2584%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=7bf86264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2851414/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E9%A1%9B%E5%80%92%EF%BC%9F%E7%BE%8E%E5%AA%92%EF%BC%9AFacebook%20%E6%AD%A3%E6%8A%84%E8%A5%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B</a>"},{"pid":"328cf77d2f1d0fe229e9b47edd92fe27149bff73","tid":2365763,"uid":367280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:28:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb3c62892f8c3f807a0f24478e999eb657c4b273","tid":2365763,"uid":19437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"Suckerberg 為上位不擇手段<br />\n似足港共個聶德權咁，做第一個刀手搞侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6e214be5ea1e674846bd842c68d4df545da05f","tid":2365763,"uid":113929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:30:48.000Z","msg":"自己人，唔存在抄唔抄襲問題"},{"pid":"39d755b36145385261673ec43116fec6b6b64bad","tid":2365763,"uid":244797,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"facebook本身都係豬西洗抄同學抄番黎<br />\n搶唔到就抄都符合佢性格<br />\n介佢本質上都係一個中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b110b067ef50611d89cdc1cf122a3d768c09ab","tid":2365763,"uid":294578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"抄撚埋中国個政治審查"},{"pid":"4d25b248eb6c1befaa9865d61ed7f9b5fa31aff3","tid":2365763,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"連獨裁方面都抄襲埋添"},{"pid":"ae605056db0d18a1a325526120465535a71c62b3","tid":2365763,"uid":29917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"ban account 呢個行為，直頭係中共既專利"},{"pid":"f25e5c949b67577cf246746ec266f955cb79587f","tid":2365763,"uid":120499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:36:53.000Z","msg":"係班美國本土Gen Z White Trash 用抖陰，唔係點會自我擊敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369